			<p><strong><span class="smallcaps">Marisa Handler</span></strong> is a writer, activist, and singer-songwriter living in San Francisco. Her memoir is titled <em>Loyal to the Sky: Notes from an Activist</em> (Berrett-Koehler). She spent this past June on a meditation retreat where she practiced total silence, except for the times she&rsquo;d go far into the woods and sing to the trees and salamanders.</p><a href="/contributors/marisa-handler" class="block-contributor-link link-alt small">More From This Contributor&nbsp;&#9656;</a>		</div>
